Franco Fogliato is Recognized by Worldwide Branding For Excellence in Brand Management
Mr. Fogliato earned an MBA in general management from The Open University in 2012 


    
He attributes his success to his extensive background in business    PRINGY, FRANCE, August 04, 2016 /24-7PressRelease/ -- Franco Fogliato, Senior Vice President and General Manager EMEA of Columbia Sportswear Company, has been recognized for showing dedication, leadership and excellence in brand management.

Worldwide Branding is proud to endorse the recent, notable professional efforts and accomplishments of Franco Fogliato. A member in good standing, Franco Fogliato parlays 20 years of experience into his professional network, and has been noted for achievements, leadership abilities, and the credentials they have provided in association with their Worldwide Branding membership.

Previously a chief executive officer of a sporting goods retailer from 2004 to 2013, Franco Fogliato now serves as Senior Vice President and General Manager EMEA of Columbia Sportswear Company, a manufacturing company that provides outdoor apparel and products. Over the past 20 years, Mr. Fogliato has honed his skills in brand management, marketing and distribution, and applies them to developing effective business strategies, reporting to the international chief executive officer and serving on the executive board.

Mr. Fogliato earned an MBA in general management from The Open University in 2012 and supports various charitable organizations. He attributes his success to his extensive background in business, and looking ahead, Mr. Fogliato plans to experience continued professional growth.

Worldwide Branding has added Franco Fogliato to their distinguished Registry of Executives, Professionals and Entrepreneurs. While inclusion in Worldwide Branding is an honor, only small selections of members in each discipline are endorsed and promoted as leaders in their professional fields.About Worldwide Branding
For more than 15 years, Worldwide Branding has been the leading, one-stop-shop, personal branding company, in the United States and abroad. From writing professional biographies and press releases, to creating and driving Internet traffic to personal websites, our team of branding experts tailor each product specifically for our clients' needs. From health care to finance to education and law, our constituents represent every major industry and occupation, at all career levels.

